    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a mechanic or someone looking for a project car. The engine is currently struggling with a rough idle and several visible fluid leaks, and the transmission engagement is inconsistent. Cosmetically, the exterior shows significant wear, including rust spots and faded paint, while the interior requires a deep clean and repair of torn upholstery. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed.",
      "price": 4800.0,
