    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a fully documented service history, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure peak torsional rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise shift gates, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The chassis is free of oxidation, with all suspension bushings and dampening components maintaining factory tolerances. The exterior retains its deep luster with no paint metered outside of OEM specifications, while the interior displays zero bolster wear or trim delamination. A mechanically flawless, turnkey example for the serious enthusiast.",
